Vasilis Ntouros is a PhD student in the [https://digitalcivics.io/ Digital Civics] programme led by [https://openlab.ncl.ac.uk/ Open Lab], Newcastle University, focusing on human-computer interaction (HCI), social and ubiquitous computing. Vasilis is interested in the commons, digital learning, and the do-it-yourself/do-it-ourselves movement. He is involved in the [http://www.p2plab.gr/en/archives/1119 Phygital project]. He has also participated in a few poetry projects and he has been experimenting with forms of concrete poetry.

